div.div: Commented on #12978 [Last version - 4.12.0 (85629)] Docker Desktop failed to start on Windows

Try restarting the "LxssManager" service. That seemed to get it to start for me. It took a min the first time after restarting the service but I've had no issues since and Docker Desktop seems to start fine on it's own again.
